OL,3,C'He wasn't accountable to anyone':
OL,4,CFailures to discipline Neil Foden
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,F"There were red flags. He was not
OL,8,Fchallenged by the governors,"
OL,9,Faccording to one member of staff who
OL,10,Fhas known Neil Foden for decades.
OL,12,FS4C's flagship current affairs
OL,13,Fprogramme Y Byd ar Bedwar understands
OL,14,Fthat union members at Ysgol Friars in
OL,15,FBangor, Gwynedd, have passed a vote of
OL,16,Fno confidence in the school's
OL,17,Fgovernors following the conviction of
OL,18,Ftheir former headteacher, Neil Foden.
