OL,3,C'He wasn't accountable to anyone':
OL,4,CFailures to discipline Neil Foden
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FOn 15 May, Foden was found guilty of
OL,8,Fsexually abusing four girls over a
OL,9,Ffour-year period. He is due to be
OL,10,Fsentenced on 1 July.
OL,12,FNo information has been released about
OL,13,Fhow Neil Foden knew the girls that he
OL,14,Fabused.
OL,16,FFoden was a familiar face often
OL,17,Fdiscussing educational matters as part
OL,18,Fof his role as headteacher of Ysgol
OL,19,FFriars, Bangor. He was later appointed
OL,20,Fas strategic head at Ysgol Dyffryn
OL,21,FNantlle.
