OL,3,C'He wasn't accountable to anyone':
OL,4,CFailures to discipline Neil Foden
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FIn a special programme, a colleague of
OL,8,FFoden at Ysgol Friars has revealed
OL,9,Fthat staff at the school have lost all
OL,10,Ffaith in the governing body following
OL,11,Fthe conviction.
OL,13,FThe school's governing body is
OL,14,Fresponsible for making decisions on
OL,15,Fbehalf of the school and disciplining
OL,16,Fteachers when necessary.
OL,18,F'No one challenged him'
