OL,3,C'He wasn't accountable to anyone':
OL,4,CFailures to discipline Neil Foden
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe member of staff, and union member,
OL,8,Fwho wishes to remain anonymous, told
OL,9,Fthe programme: "They (the teachers)
OL,10,Fhave no faith at all. They unanimously
OL,11,Fhave no faith in the current governing
OL,12,Fbody."
OL,14,FThey say the governing body failed in
OL,15,Ftheir responsibility to discipline
OL,16,FNeil Foden after he was found to have
OL,17,Fcommitted unacceptable professional
OL,18,Fconduct by the Education Workforce
OL,19,FCouncil in 2020.
