OL,3,C'He wasn't accountable to anyone':
OL,4,CFailures to discipline Neil Foden
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FDuring the hearing, the panel heard
OL,8,Fthat almost all of the staff at the
OL,9,Fschool had signed a letter supporting
OL,10,FNeil Foden.
OL,12,FIn 2018, a different member of staff
OL,13,Fat Ysgol Friars, Simon Wilson, won an
OL,14,Femployment tribunal case against Neil
OL,15,FFoden. The biology teacher was given
OL,16,F#8,000 in compensation for the way he
OL,17,Fwas treated by the former headteacher.
OL,19,FThis came after Mr Wilson raised his
OL,20,Fconcerns about the falsification of
OL,21,Fexam results at Ysgol Friars in 2014.
