OL,3,C'He wasn't accountable to anyone':
OL,4,CFailures to discipline Neil Foden
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FIn an email, Neil Foden told Mr Wilson
OL,8,Fhe would be protected against the
OL,9,FPublic Interest Disclosure Act, and
OL,10,Fwould therefore not be punished for
OL,11,Fraising concerns.
OL,13,FAccording to Simon's wife Lesley
OL,14,FWilson, this was not the case.
OL,16,FShe told the programme: "My husband
OL,17,Fwas bullied and harassed by Foden over
OL,18,Fa period of four years, he was
OL,19,Fdisciplined twice and suspended over a
OL,20,Ffalse allegation."
