OL,3,C'He wasn't accountable to anyone':
OL,4,CFailures to discipline Neil Foden
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FShe said: "Foden should have at least
OL,8,Fbeen disciplined. I feel he was given
OL,9,Fthe opportunity to feel more
OL,10,Fauthoritative and powerful and that
OL,11,Fempowered him to go on to commit these
OL,12,Foffences against those children.
OL,14,F"Neil Foden wasn't accountable to
OL,15,Fanybody. It's very sad that it's taken
OL,16,Fsome young girls to stand up to Foden
OL,17,Fand hold him responsible. And all
OL,18,Fthese men in positions of
OL,19,Fresponsibility were not prepared to
OL,20,Fstand up to Neil Foden."
