OL,4,CFailures to discipline Neil Foden
OL,5,Crevealed
OL,7,FThe staff member said "the only thing
OL,8,Fthey have received is the records that
OL,9,Fhave been completely redacted, all of
OL,10,Fthe discussions have been redacted. We
OL,11,Fhave no idea what has been discussed.
OL,12,FSeveral requests had to be sent to the
OL,13,Fauthority.
OL,15,F"What are they trying to hide?"
OL,17,FChair of governors stands down
