OL,7,FHe added: "We concluded that the right
OL,8,Ftime to leave is now."
OL,10,FIn response to Simon Wilson's
OL,11,Ftribunal, Mr Ahari said the governors
OL,12,Freceived advice from the local
OL,13,Fauthority and that an independent
OL,14,Fperson was appointed to look at the
OL,15,Fschool's processes as a part of their
OL,16,Fattempt to learn lessons.
