OL,7,FPrior to his resignation Mr Ahari said
OL,8,Fon behalf of the governing body that
OL,9,Fthey collectively appreciate the
OL,10,Fdedication of staff over the last
OL,11,Fmonths and that specialist support
OL,12,Fservices continued to be on offer at
OL,13,FYsgol Friars for anyone who needs them.
OL,15,F'Lessons to be learnt'
OL,17,FCyngor Gwynedd Council has announced
OL,18,Fthat the North Wales Safeguarding
OL,19,FBoard is conducting a review to look
OL,20,Finto the events involving Neil Foden.
