OL,7,F"With the criminal process drawing to
OL,8,Fa close, the work of reviewing and
OL,9,Festablishing what lessons are to be
OL,10,Flearnt from the case has started, and
OL,11,Fthe North Wales Safeguarding Board
OL,12,Fhave said that they want to carry out
OL,13,Fa child practice review, in line with
OL,14,Fthe national children's practice
OL,15,Freview guidelines."
